{"tid":1042224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豐田被罵翻  在推特問女駕駛是否不太會開車","createTime":"2019-03-01T11:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T12:17:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19c94e8fd805ef5340666a71248fe14408872b40","tid":1042224,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"2019-03-01 17:46<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本豐田汽車被罵慘了！其官方推特在今天（1日）的PO文中，詢問女性駕駛是否不太會開車，立即遭到網友連番砲轟，豐田見事情不妙連忙刪除貼文並道歉。<br />\n<br />\n據《朝日新聞》報導，豐田汽車當時透過推特的投票功能，PO出了以下提問：「想問各位女駕駛一個問題，開車果然是一件不太擅長的事情嗎？」接著下面有「非常不擅長」、「有點不擅長」等選項。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友隨即爆氣，怒斥「為什麼要說果然？是在歧視女性嗎？」、「為什麼只問女駕駛」，還有人感嘆，自己從取得駕照以來從來沒發生任何交通事故，如今卻要被汽車公司嗆是不是不太會開車。<br />\n<br />\n豐田汽車遭受各種評論抨擊後，連忙在今天下午4時許發出道歉聲明，坦承他們在女駕駛開車的問題上有了不適當的說法，公司方面對此表達最深切的道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713536&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=4c324c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713536&h=adb8f6f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713536</a>"},{"pid":"df7ecee783de9b508f1434e34030d2af0fba3295","tid":1042224,"uid":124491,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"講吓笑都唔撚俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8626694f2147738c71ca4bdd5d5708b1c50477b","tid":1042224,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"No place for gender inequality 😡😡"},{"pid":"69bd211630596b4aee018dbc3eec31709ef44948","tid":1042224,"uid":143241,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"女人連ATM都用唔掂,仲想揸車?"},{"pid":"e0594be0a41cdfc7ce391c05a06035f431f8a1fd","tid":1042224,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":